@page "/resources"

<h1>Resources</h1>

<div class="accordion" id="resourcesAccordion">
    <!-- Section 1: For The Students -->
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                &#x2193; For The Students
            </button>
        </h2>
        <!-- Description for Section 1 -->
        <div class="accordion-body">
            <p>This section contains key online platforms and tools that Missouri S&T students use to manage their academic and personal information, access campus resources, and stay connected with the university community.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#resourcesAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="http://joess.mst.edu/" target="_blank">Joe'SS (Student Self-Service)</a>
                        <p class="text-muted">Joe'SS is Missouri S&T's online portal for students to manage their academic records, register for classes, view grades, and access financial information.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://minerlink.mst.edu/home_login" target="_blank">MinerLink</a>
                        <p class="text-muted">MinerLink is Missouri S&T's platform for students to connect with campus organizations, explore events, and engage with the university community.</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 2: Student Health & Well-Being -->
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                &#x2193; Student Health & Well-Being
            </button>
        </h2>
        <!-- Description for Section 2 -->
        <div class="accordion-body">
            <p>In this section, you'll find resources focused on supporting students' physical and mental health, offering everything from medical services to wellness programs and mental health counseling.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#resourcesAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="http://mst.studenthealthportal.com/" target="_blank">Student Health Portal</a>
                        <p class="text-muted">The Student Health Portal provides Missouri S&T students with secure access to their health records, appointment scheduling, and communication with campus health services.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://wellbeing.mst.edu/services/" target="_blank">Student Well-Being Services</a>
                        <p class="text-muted">The Student Well-Being Services at Missouri S&T offer resources and support for mental health, wellness, and personal development, providing counseling, workshops, and wellness activities to help students thrive.</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 3: Academic Achievement & Enrichment -->
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                &#x2193; Academic Achievement & Enrichment
            </button>
        </h2>
        <!-- Description for Section 3 -->
        <div class="accordion-body">
            <p>This section provides resources designed to help students succeed academically, including tutoring services, study strategies, and academic advising. It also includes platforms that help students track their academic progress and access additional learning support</p>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#resourcesAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://advising.mst.edu/handbook/academicsupportservices/" target="_blank">Academic Support Services</a>
                        <p class="text-muted">Missouri S&T's Academic Support Services offers various resources to help students succeed academically, including tutoring, writing assistance, study strategies, and workshops to enhance learning and academic performance.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://mst.starfishsolutions.com/starfish-ops/support/login.html" target="_blank">Starfish Student Success Portal(S&T Connect?)</a>
                        <p class="text-muted">(Note Refresh the Page after clicking link, may have to find another one)Starfish is a platform that connects students with academic resources, advising, and support services at Missouri S&T. It helps track progress, request help, and schedule appointments with advisors and tutors.</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
